      },
      "description": "Where did the ATTRIBUTED money go? Each rectangle is a WMS entity, sized by cost and colored by status (green=done, blue=active, yellow=review, red=blocked, gray=legacy). Legacy v1 entities show as explicit (legacy <type>) rectangles per the locked label convention. Unallocated cost is excluded here (it would dominate ~69% of the area) — the Unallocated Cost stat and the Attribution Coverage Trend carry that full-picture honesty. Rendered via the Business Charts (ECharts) plugin.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {},
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 11,
